name: Jobquest International Jobs
tag_list: international-jobs, jobquest, work-permit, job-visa, overseas-jobs, employment-abroad, careers, graduate-programs, recruiters-directory
overview: Jobquest International Jobs is an social networking platform for international recruitment and career. Online since year 2004. Jobquest offers jobseekers to create resume, search jobs, work permit, job visa, expatriate jobs, apply jobs, communicate with employers/ recruiters. Offer recruiters to recruit, take online interview, post jobs, share information to memebers. Jobquest also publish international recruitment, career, work permit news from all over the world. Free to join. Other features are career resources, gap year opportunities, graduate programs, cv development guidelines, cv/ resume pushing to hidden job market,
